      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;november-5-2024&#34;&gt;November 5, 2024&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;building-an-ai-chatbot-with-xai&#34;&gt;Building an AI Chatbot with xAI&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://x.com/xai/status/1853505214181232828&#34;&gt;xAI just released their API&lt;/a&gt; and through the end of the year you can get $25 in credits each month. I took it for a quick spin and set up a chatbot using NextJS and Deepgram.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The first step was to create an xAI account and generate an API key:
&lt;img alt=&#34;xAI API Console&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/posts/microblog/microblog-11-05-2024/image.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Then, spin up a quick NextJS web page that uses the &lt;a href=&#34;https://sdk.vercel.ai/&#34;&gt;AI SDK&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
